          5-YEARS-OLDS WITH THEIR FAMILIES

"AMAZING BUILDING" FRENCH STORYTELLING TOUR FOR 3 TO 5-YEARS-OLDS WITH THEIR
FAMILIES

          FROM 11.30 A.M. TO 12.30 P.M. - SATURDAYS AND SUNDAYS
          FROM 31 AUGUST TO 28 SEPTEMBER 2019
          In French only
          Children and parents follow the adventures of a small falcon
          flying over the Foundation looking for the amazing secrets of
          the building.

